title: Trang Municipality Stadium
text: Trang Municipality Stadium or Trang Provincial Stadium () is a <a href="multi-purpose%20stadium">multi-purpose stadium</a> in <a href="Trang%20Province">Trang Province</a>, <a href="Thailand">Thailand</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Trang%20F.C.">Trang F.C.</a>.
